# === STUDENT-BUILD METADATA — NOT shipped in the workshop bootstrap package ===
# Students author the agent, eval suite, Data Library, Experience Cloud site,
# and MIAW deployment as part of the workshop exercises. These directories
# exist in source for facilitator end-state demos (install.sh) but are
# excluded from the unlocked-package bootstrap that students install.
# Phase 5 deploy override: aiAuthoringBundles/ temporarily un-ignored so the
# .agent metadata-deploy path can run. Restore this rule after Phase 5 settles.
# force-app/main/default/aiAuthoringBundles/
force-app/main/default/aiEvaluationDefinitions/
force-app/main/default/genAiPlannerBundles/
force-app/main/default/bots/
# Site metadata — Salesforce 2GP packaging rejects DigitalExperienceBundle ("not
# compatible with site workspaces"). The Electra portal bundle is tracked in
# source but excluded from the unlocked-package build. Facilitators deploy the
# bundle separately via `sf project deploy start` from this repo.
force-app/main/default/digitalExperiences/
force-app/main/default/messagingChannels/
force-app/main/default/EmbeddedServiceConfig/
force-app/main/default/brandingSets/
